{
 "name": "RPlog_Piper_s_Guards_Shoot_Kuxli",
 "title": "Piper's Guards Shoot Kuxli",
 "summary": "On Hideaway Beach near Plaxton on Caspar, the CSA VicePrex Piper coldly looks on as her Espo guards open fire on the young Horansi cub Kuxli. Wounded and panicking, Kuxli bolts for the road crying for help, only to be cut down by repeated blaster bolts until he collapses unmoving in the sand. Unmoved and scowling, Piper orders the Espos to drag the unconscious cub to her ship, and the procession of guards hauling his limp body makes its way through Plaxton's Fountain Square -- past a startled witness, Vance -- toward the spaceport. The brutal scene underscores Piper's ruthless devotion to the Authority's interests.",
